      <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=487148&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;mobile=2">9.18，日本人在山西的罪行，勿忘国耻</a>
     </div> 
     <!-- more pagelist start --> 
     <div class="plc cl" id="pid1952726"> 
      <div class="display pi"> 
       <div class="authi"> 
        <img class="avatar" src="http://www.linfen365.com/uc_server/avatar.php?uid=35507&amp;size=small" /> 
